WEBVTT

00:06:29.029 --> 00:06:30.514
I'm just overreacting.

00:06:30.538 --> 00:06:31.866
I'm totally overreacting."

00:06:31.890 --> 00:06:33.040
No.

00:06:33.719 --> 00:06:34.869
No.

00:06:35.508 --> 00:06:36.658
No.

00:06:37.244 --> 00:06:39.929
No, no, no, no, no.

00:06:40.988 --> 00:06:45.497
Women have been trained
to think that we are overreacting

00:06:45.521 --> 00:06:49.246
or that we're being too sensitive
or unreasonable.

00:06:49.270 --> 00:06:51.097
We try to make sense of nonsense,

00:06:51.121 --> 00:06:53.405
and we swallow the furious feelings.

00:06:53.429 --> 00:06:56.749
We try to put them into
some hidden place in our minds,

00:06:56.773 --> 00:06:58.261
but they don't go away.

00:06:59.794 --> 00:07:04.509
That fury sits deep inside
as we practice our smiles --